President Cyril Ramaphosa addresses the National Summit on Science and Innovation response to COVID-19. President Ramaphosa will share the platform with World Health Organisation (WHO) Director-General Dr Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus. Under the theme “Harnessing science, technology and innovation in response to COVID-19: A national and international effort”, the Summit will focus on health innovation and technologies, and social and economic sustainability during and after the pandemic. Below is the live stream: 